️遮陣位：正門<br />\n☂️還押後獲釋遮陣位：正門<br />\n🚐送車位：正門轉右再轉右行幾級樓梯，兜到去消防局停車場<br />\n<br />\n<strong>《東 區 裁 判 法 院》</strong><br />\n☂️遮陣位：正門<br />\n☂️還押後獲釋遮陣位：正門<br />\n🚐送車位：正門轉左再轉左（巴士站對面）<br />\n<br />\n<strong>《九 龍 城 裁 判 法 院》</strong><br />\n☂️遮陣位：正門／其他秘道<br />\n☂️還押後獲釋遮陣位：行去送車位既通道有間房仔<br />\n🚐送車位：正門轉左再轉左（小馬路）<br />\n<br />\n<strong>《屯 門 裁 判 法 院》</strong><br />\n☂️遮陣位：正門<br />\n☂️還押後獲釋遮陣位：正門<br />\n🚐送車位：正門轉左（送車口好細）<br />\n<br />\n<strong>特別鳴謝被捕人士關注組公海手足cc整合以上資訊</strong>"},{"pid":"7ce1bba7f76d0f7b3a9cdc276888460b3027c2d8","tid":2024230,"uid":223208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T13:19:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a00e77851e2b84fcd70789f9e182f758cd9b1360","tid":2024230,"uid":69916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T13:19:32.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b7086626db50aefba2c50a4ce30a61fd75c2a2d4","tid":2024230,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T13:19:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fac556c851fdc2a8312698784472c213c74a7497","tid":2024230,"uid":223208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T13:20:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"16bb305190efb35b657e99d45049e58db65812ae","tid":2024230,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T13:20:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"255445457b1c2c8cacf85d5fdb469b57fd2c1305","tid":2024230,"uid":62259,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T13:20:38.000Z","msg":"標準做法:<br />\n推 上一頁<br />\n唔去"},{"pid":"0790ccb9aae4e175cbe604eaf6146d7b94cf6b73","tid":2024230,"uid":223208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T13:21:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces